object.name: Agents
object.simulatedExtractionQuery:
SELECT *
AGENT_EVENT AGENT_EVENT,
  AGENT_EVENT_DETAILS aed,
  AGENT a
WHERE
  ae.AGENT_EVENT_GID = aed.AGENT_EVENT_GID
  AND aed.AGENT_GID = a.AGENT_GID
  AND ae.DOMAIN_NAME = 'BAU'
  AND a.IS_ACTIVE = 'Y'
ORDER BY
  ae.DATA_QUERY_TYPE_GID,
  ae.AGENT_EVENT_XID,
  a.AGENT_XID

extraction.query:

FROM
  AGENT_EVENT ae,
  AGENT_EVENT_DETAILS aed,
  AGENT a
WHERE

  AND ae.DOMAIN_NAME = 'BAU'
  AND a.IS_ACTIVE = 'Y'
ORDER BY
  ae.DATA_QUERY_TYPE_GID,
  ae.AGENT_EVENT_XID,
  a.AGENT_XID

AGENTE DE ORQUESTRACAO DISPARADO NA CRIACAO DA PARADA (SHIPMENT_STOP).
